caption: Wow.  I mean,  like... wow.  Fillet Minion cooked medium well to perfection,  paired exquisitely with I don't even remember what she said, and a chocolate syrup sundae that really needed to be hot fudge.  I should have gotten that big brownie thing... next time...

This place is a gem in downtown Pleasanton.  Great place for wine, beer and great food, plus on Saturdays they have live music outdoors.  I had their butternut squash flatbread and their baked brie and they were both delicious.
